    "DeepSHAP implementations to identify a latent features/clinical variables that contribute most to the difference in PI between high-and low-risk groups, and b pathways/genes/miRNAs that contribute most to the difference in latent-feature values (between high-and low-risk groups) for the most important latent features found in (a).",
